  <prompt>Per inventory, add MembershipChangedEvent publishing to matter mutation endpoints. Fire-and-forget per Q2 — publish failure logs structured warning but does NOT roll back mutation.</prompt>
  <goal>Matter cluster endpoints publish events on lookup mutations. Tests confirm publish.</goal>
  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec Q2">Fire-and-forget semantics; publish failure logs warning + nightly recon backstop</constraint>
    <constraint source="bff-extensions.md §A">BFF pre-merge checklist</constraint>
    <constraint source="NFR-08">correlationId carried in published event</constraint>
  </constraints>
  <knowledge>
    <topic>event-publishing-service-bus</topic>
    <files>
      <file>.claude/patterns/api/background-workers.md</file>
      <file>.claude/patterns/api/error-handling.md</file>
